
Ta labels mpainoun mesa sta pods
metadata:
    Labels:
        app: App1
        funtion: Front-end


OI SELECTORS EINAI GIA NA TSIMPISOUME TA PODS ME TA LABELS
kubectl get pods --selector app=App1



Akoma Oi Selectors mpainoun mesa sta service h deployments me skopo na dilosw ta pods

spec:
    selector:
        app: App1